<section class="values">
  <div class="wrap-wide">
    <div class="values-head">
      <div>
        <span class="eyebrow">What we won't compromise on</span>
        <h2>The <em>standards</em> behind the sachet.</h2>
      </div>
      <p>Six things we decided at the start that we haven't changed since.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="values-grid">
      <div class="value"><div class="num">N°01</div><h3>Every dose on the label</h3><p>No proprietary blends. No "performance complex." If you can't see what's in the dose, you can't trust the dose.</p></div>
      <div class="value"><div class="num">N°02</div><h3>Clinical doses only</h3><p>If a study used 250mg, we put 250mg in. Not 50mg with a famous brand name. We pay the cost.</p></div>
      <div class="value"><div class="num">N°03</div><h3>Real food, not flavouring</h3><p>Real lemon. Real fruit when we expand. No "natural flavours," no artificial colours, no maskers.</p></div>
      <div class="value"><div class="num">N°04</div><h3>Tested, every batch</h3><p>Heavy metals, mineral content, banned substances. ICP-MS verified. Lab reports available on request.</p></div>
      <div class="value"><div class="num">N°05</div><h3>Subscription you can leave</h3><p>Skip, pause, cancel any time from your dashboard. No phone calls. No retention emails. No friction.</p></div>
      <div class="value"><div class="num">N°06</div><h3>The 60-day guarantee</h3><p>If it doesn't work, we refund the box. Even if you've used it. We'd rather lose the order than your trust.</p></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
